  <div class="article-byline__content">
      <div class="article-byline__written-by">
    <strong>Written by</strong> <br><strong><script>function ga4_link112() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"default_event"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/authors/tj-donegan" onclick="ga4_link112()">TJ Donegan</a></strong>, who has covered electronics, TVs, smartphones, parenting for 10+ years.<br><strong><script>function ga4_link113() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"default_event"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/authors/lily-hartman" onclick="ga4_link113()">Lily Hartman</a></strong>, staff writer, research expert, and active lifestyle enthusiast.
  </div>



    <p class="article-byline__pub-dates">
      Updated March 18, 2024
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

              <p></p>
<p>If your home has carpets then you’re bound to run into some unfortunate stains and general dinginess that your <script>function ga4_link114() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"click_inarticle"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/vacuums/best-right-now/the-best-vacuums-of-every-type" onclick="ga4_link114()">normal vacuum</a> can't touch. While a basic shampoo or spot cleaner can help lift a stain out, the best carpet cleaners will consistently do a better job. </p>

<p>These dedicated machines are like the ones you rent, with motors and brush heads like vacuums. The difference? The best carpet cleaners for your home are designed to mix detergent and water, scrubbing out tough stains before sucking up the dirty water.</p>

<p>They’re extremely effective at removing even nasty stains and are a critical part of keeping your carpets clean year after year, and unlike with rented models, when you own your own carpet cleaner, you won't find someone else's gunk stuck to the bottom.</p>

<p>If you’re shopping for a carpet cleaner to deep clean your home, you’ve come to the right place. We’ve looked into a number of carpet cleaners and generally found them easy to operate and effective at cleaning your carpets and removing odors. And while you’ll pay a little extra compared to when you rent a machine, after just two or three uses most of these machines—even the pro-grade ones—will pay for themselves.</p>

<p>Here are our top picks for the best carpet cleaner machines you can get online right now.
</p>
<div>
  <figure data-image-attachment>
    <figure class="image-wrapper">
      <img alt="A large Bissell sits on a green Reviewed background." class="lazyload blur-up attachment" eager="false" data-portal-copyright="Reviewed / Bissell" data-src="https://reviewed-com-res.cloudinary.com/image/fetch/s--qu-2FHKw--/b_white,c_limit,cs_srgb,f_auto,fl_progressive.strip_profile,g_center,q_auto,w_792/https://reviewed-production.s3.amazonaws.com/attachment/4c47e0b077ed4b72/2.png" style="aspect-ratio: 1.78;" src="https://reviewed-com-res.cloudinary.com/image/fetch/s--dkmq0bhB--/b_white,c_limit,cs_srgb,f_auto,fl_progressive.strip_profile,g_center,q_1,w_792/https://reviewed-production.s3.amazonaws.com/attachment/4c47e0b077ed4b72/2.png">
