<p>The reviews are eye-opening, especially from people that tried other, less-powerful carpet cleaners.This machine picks up so much more debris, hair, dirt, and grime, a second pass won’t be necessary. One reviewer said that this Bissell Big Green professional carpet cleaner was one of the best purchases they’d ever made, and it’s easy to see why.</p>

