      <div class="c-product-widget__content">
      <p>The Hoover PowerDash Pet is a compact carpet cleaner with an upright design, but a relatively narrow cleaning path. It’s more affordable than some of the other cleaners on our list, and it’s ideal if you want to clean spot stains and occasionally want to tackle large areas. It’ll take some time, but it can clean tough carpets and remove lots of pet stains and odors thanks to its cleaning power.</p>

<p>The main complaints from reviewers came down to the small size of the internal tanks. If you’re trying to clean anything other than a small area, you’re going to need to plan to refill and empty the internal tanks repeatedly.</p>

