      <p>The Bissell TurboClean PowerBrush is another lightweight, compact and upright carpet cleaner that is designed to tackle small area rugs, carpets, and spot stains. It has a dual clean water tank design so you’re not cleaning with dirty water, but the tanks are just over a half gallon so they tend to fill up quickly, as with other compact uprights.</p>

<p>Reviewers highly recommend this cleaner, with thousands of 5-star reviews that show just how clean this can get your carpet and upholstery. It may be small, but it’s still a powerful cleaner that can get the job done without weighing you down.</p>

